    <item>
      <title>Meta、X、TikTok 首席执行官因儿童网络安全问题遭到参议员批评</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/meta-x-tiktok-ceos-face-us-senate-on-protecting-kids-online</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国参议院讨论儿童在线安全的听证会上，五个社交媒体平台的领导人受到立法者的训诫，立法者抨击了这些公司过去为保护儿童所做的努力，并敦促他们支持新的立法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/meta-x-tiktok-ceos-face-us-senate-on-protecting-kids-online</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 14:36:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国寻求通过修改贸易计划来结束北爱尔兰僵局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/uk-plans-to-ease-gb-n-ireland-trade-flows-to-restore-stormont</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国公布了一项减少从英国流向北爱尔兰的货物贸易摩擦的计划，此举预计将说服民主统一党结束对该地区权力下放政府的两年抵制，尽管该计划尚未达成重大协议彻底修改英国脱欧规则。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/uk-plans-to-ease-gb-n-ireland-trade-flows-to-restore-stormont</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 13:18:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
